    "Id": "500905",
    "ThreadId": "229263",
    "Html": "<p>Hi there,</p>\r\n<p>I am trying to style a grid of mine so that an image is being displayed depending of the value of the ﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿DataGridCheckBoxColumn. The default is to display a checkbox, but I want to replace the checkbox with a red or green image.</p>\r\n<p>I have search around but wasn't too successful in find samples. If I do find something, I will post it here.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks in advance.</p>",
